BTCSERV.net was a free for all [[Mining Pool|Pooled_Mining]] with proportional [[Bitcoin]] payouts located in Germany. The pool was launched on July 9th, 2011 and its features were [[Long_Polling]], SSL encrypted user interface and fast payouts. Only the [[transaction fee|transaction_fees]] were kept by the pool operator.

